title: Cleaning Guy with No Perspective
description:
Your father liked me to vacuum.

Starring Jonathan Marballi, Dan Hodapp, and Avery Monsen
Written by Zack Phillips
Directed by Jim Santangeli
Shot and Edited by Alex Adan

Taped on January 30th, 2012
